title: Dictionary from Lingvo 12 [6 language] for StarDict [platform in
description:
Abbyy Lingvo 12 dictionarys in StarDict format
 
Developer of original dictioanarys homepage http//www.lingvo.ru/
System requements: StarDict for any platform, 1,12 GB free space
 
Description These dictionaries were convert from the program-dictionary "Abbyy lingvo 12 Multilingual Edition ". To do this, at the beginning, using the modified DSLComp.exe (attached to the distribution) were convert dictionaries in the format dsl. After that, from dsl  to Stardict format using makedict_0.3.
Ability to pronounce the word for these dictionaries absent.
For installing dictionarys do next
Unpack archives to directorys
For Linux /usr/share/stardict/dic
For Windows C\Program Files\stardict\dic
For Mac OS X /opt/gtk/usr/share/stardict/dic
 
List of dictionarys:
Dutch-Russian and Russian-Germany dictionarys
English-English dictionarys
English-Russian and Russian-English dictionarys
French-Russian and Russian-French dictionarys
Italian-Russian and Russian-Italiaan dictinarys
Russian-Russian dictinarys
Spanish-Russian and Russian-Spanish dictionarys
Ukrainian-English and English-ukrainian dictioanrys
Ukrainia-Ukrainian dictioanrys
